FORGEZERO EXAMPLES
===================

SINGLE-FILE C BUILD
-------------------
fz -cc main.c

ASSEMBLY BUILD WITH RAW LINK MODE
--------------------------------
fz --set mode=raw -asm kernel.asm -out kernel.bin

PROJECT WITH TOML CONFIG
------------------------
output = "demo"
source_dirs = ["src"]
profile = "balanced"

CROSS-COMPILE EXAMPLE
---------------------
fz -target aarch64-linux-gnu -cc main.c
